text:
TV Magazine TERROR IN THE TOON Geordie Shore stars pictured stumbling in to the street after being rushed to safety as man plunges through roof of Newcastle’s Tup Tup nightclub 
Marnie Simpson looked worse for wear as she stumbled bare-foot while Chloe came narrowly close to a wardrobe malfunction By REBECCA POCKLINGTON
